{"tid":1634270,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"18區再開花！ 網民號召今日下午3時「全民V煞」    高喊：香港人反抗到底","createTime":"2019-10-07T07:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T16:23:49.000Z","uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7e21ac4e47ed95eab86fd842420ea2155331846","tid":1634270,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:10:13.000Z","msg":"【果燃台直擊】18區再開花！ 網民號召「全民V煞」 高喊：香港人反抗到底<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191007/large/1570424030_11fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191007%2Flarge%2F1570424030_11fd.jpg&h=ab885468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府上周五（4日）宣佈引用《緊急法》強推《蒙面法》後，連日來的示威遍地開花，「香港人，反抗」的叫喊聲響遍18區。繼昨日（6日）全民佩戴口罩遊行，反抗惡法後，再有網民號召市民今日下午3時，在全港18區響應「全民V煞」，呼籲「香港人反抗到底！」《蘋果》將直擊各區情況，適時現場直播。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191007/60126098\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191007%2F60126098&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn%2FjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=25c6106a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191007%2F60126098&h=f3841c9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191007/60126098</a>"},{"pid":"e2d92391d5010262644a9bd76a9e8097a3a344ab","tid":1634270,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:10:42.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"cd110bd09178028640dcc05d5f98fdb386d6b542","tid":1634270,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:11:38.000Z","msg":"721  811  831   101"},{"pid":"74f95c66853f13356afd8df9de12d276ec1192dc","tid":1634270,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good